OL,3,CMan who murdered son's girlfriend in
OL,4,C'frenzied attack' gets life sentence
OL,6,FA man has been sentenced to life after
OL,7,Fmurdering his son's girlfriend.
OL,9,FRichard Jones killed Sophie Evans in
OL,10,Fher home on 5 July 2024 after falsely
OL,11,Fclaiming his son and Ms Evans had
OL,12,Fswindled him out of money.
OL,14,FAt Swansea Court Court, Judge Geraint
OL,15,FWalters told the defendant he had
OL,16,Flaunched a "sustained and frenzied
OL,17,Fattack on a woman wearing a towel in
OL,18,Fher own home."
