OL,3,CMan who murdered son's girlfriend in
OL,4,C'frenzied attack' gets life sentence
OL,6,FAbul Hussain of the Crown Prosecution
OL,7,FService said: "The evidence presented
OL,8,Fto the jury demonstrated that Richard
OL,9,FJones bore full responsibility for his
OL,10,Fcallous actions.
OL,12,F"Our thoughts remain with Sophie's
OL,13,Ffamily and friends over their tragic
OL,14,Floss."
OL,16,FToday Swansea Crown Court heard a
OL,17,Fvictim impact statement from the
OL,18,Fsister of Sophie Evans. Kerry Quinlan
OL,19,Fsaid "words could not express" how
OL,20,Fmuch her two young children miss her.
